<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"> <channel><title>望薮</title><description>明日巴陵道，秋山又几重。</description><link>https://ralvines.top/</link><atom:link href="https://ralvines.top/feed_rss_updated.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" /><language>en</language> <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 01:11:09 -0000</pubDate> <lastBuildDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 01:11:09 -0000</lastBuildDate> <ttl>1440</ttl> <generator>MkDocs RSS plugin - v1.6.0</generator> <item> <title>一路向北：厦门、南京故地重游记</title> <category>2024-03-30</category> <category>旅途</category> <description>...</description><link>https://ralvines.top/diary/fujian/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 23:16:26 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://ralvines.top/feed_rss_updated.xml">望薮</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://ralvines.top/diary/fujian/</guid> </item> <item> <title>四月随想：与时舒卷</title> <category>2023-04-22</category> <category>随想</category> <description>突然间，我意识到这样一件事实——自己是“非常需要进入状态”的一类人。</description><link>https://ralvines.top/diary/siyue/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 23:16:26 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://ralvines.top/feed_rss_updated.xml">望薮</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://ralvines.top/diary/siyue/</guid> </item> <item> <title>刘慈欣短篇：科幻抑或近代史诗</title> <category>2022-12-01</category> <category>文学</category> <description>在刘慈欣的文学世界里，种种物理猜想和对世界本原的思索不仅是世界观的需要，也是叙事的重心本身。</description><link>https://ralvines.top/mindkit/liucixin/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 23:16:26 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://ralvines.top/feed_rss_updated.xml">望薮</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://ralvines.top/mindkit/liucixin/</guid> </item> <item> <title>设计师的政治人生</title> <category>2023-10-31</category> <category>政治</category> <description>正如他在三十年前写下的，在现代个人主义文化的弘扬过程中，个人获得了自由，但是却孤独了。</description><link>https://ralvines.top/mindkit/political-life/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 23:16:26 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://ralvines.top/feed_rss_updated.xml">望薮</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://ralvines.top/mindkit/political-life/</guid> </item> <item> <title>华灯初上、春和景明与久违晴天</title> <category>2024-03-08</category> <category>旅途</category> <description>从除夕到元宵，由玄冬向立春，镜头里是新年以来的的一点剪影。</description><link>https://ralvines.top/diary/sunnyday/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 16:27:32 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://ralvines.top/feed_rss_updated.xml">望薮</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://ralvines.top/diary/sunnyday/</guid> <enclosure url="https://s21.ax1x.com/2024/03/08/pFsVAPI.jpg" type="image/jpeg" length="798892" /> </item> <item> <title>火车开往破晓</title> <category>2023-05-04</category> <category>旅途</category> <description>「昔人已乘黄鹤去，此地空余黄鹤楼。」五一前夕，一个念头在脑海中迸发：之前走过东西南北的不同省份，却唯独忘记了华中这片土地。于是，这趟行程就此展开。</description><link>https://ralvines.top/diary/wuhan/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 16:27:32 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://ralvines.top/feed_rss_updated.xml">望薮</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://ralvines.top/diary/wuhan/</guid> <enclosure url="https://pic.imgdb.cn/item/655c9426c458853aefc572c8.jpg" type="image/jpeg" length="56417" /> </item> <item> <title>告别完美主义幻想</title> <category>2023-04-17</category> <category>心理</category> <description>相比于同不同类型的人们打交道，或许我们更难以面对的是如何与自身相处。</description><link>https://ralvines.top/mindkit/taobi/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 16:27:32 +0000</pubDate><source url="https://ralvines.top/feed_rss_updated.xml">望薮</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://ralvines.top/mindkit/taobi/</guid> </item> </channel></rss>